claim.claim-text:
4. The method according to claim 2 and further including: 
a. coupling inputs of said test probe to an transition printed circuit board having a pattern of contact points the same as the pattern on said printed circuit board; 
b. supporting said spring loaded contacts in a block; 
c. supporting said block, said test probe and said transition printed circuit board in a housing; 
d. coupling said spring loaded contacts to said contact points on said transition printed circuit board; and 
e. engaging the alignment guides on the printed circuit board with alignment guides coupled to said housing.
